    "asOf": "2009-09-22",
    "date": "2009-09-28T20:09:17Z",
    "text": "Home Office Deduction Simplification Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a taxpayer who uses a residence to conduct a trade or business a standard tax deduction equal to the lesser of $1,500 or the taxpayer's gross trade or business income derived from the business use of such residence."
